== CONSTANTS ==

• COS_30      - cos(30°) ≈ 0.866
• COS_30_INV  - 1/cos(30°) ≈ 1.155

== FUNCTIONS ==

• skewY(points, deg, zeroOffset)
    Vertical shear on array of Points.

• scaleX(size, factor) / scaleY(size, factor)
    Scale Size horizontally/vertically.

• getAllGraphics(graphic)
    Flatten groups into array of leaf graphics.

• applySkewY(graphic, deg, [zeroOffset])
    Vertical skew on graphic. Supports shapes and lines.

• applyScale(graphic, axis, factor)
    Scale bounding box. axis: 'x' or 'y'

• makePlane(graphic, planeType, [zeroOffset])
    Isometric transform. planeType: 'left', 'right', 'topLeft', 'topRight'

• getSharedMinX(graphics)
    Compute combined bounding box minX for multiple graphics.

• applySkewYMulti(graphics, deg)
    Apply skew to multiple graphics with shared zeroOffset.

• makePlaneMulti(graphics, planeType)
    Transform multiple graphics as a unit.

• duplicateGraphics(canvas, graphics)
    Duplicate graphics on canvas.

• duplicateAndMakePlane(canvas, graphics, planeType)
    Duplicate and transform in one step.
